---
/* Global Edge - All 4 Languages Integrated */
---
<section id="advantage" class="global-advantage">
    <h2 class="text-gradient">The Multilingual Mastery</h2>
    <div class="language-showcase">
        <div class="lang-card"><h3>English</h3><p>Universal Reach for a global audience.</p></div>
        <div class="lang-card highlight"><h3>Tamil | தமிழ்</h3><p>Community Authority and local trust.</p></div>
        <div class="lang-card highlight-mandarin"><h3>Mandarin | 普通话</h3><p>Global Investment and international networks.</p></div>
        <div class="lang-card"><h3>Spanish | Español</h3><p>Expanding into fast-growing markets.</p></div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .global-advantage { padding: 6rem 5%; text-align: center; }
    .text-gradient { background: linear-gradient(to right, #34d399, #a3e635); -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 800; }
    .language-showcase { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; margin-top: 3rem; }
    .lang-card { padding: 2.5rem; background: #0d1224; border-radius: 24px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); text-align: left; }
    .highlight { border-color: #fbbf24; }
    .highlight-mandarin { border-color: #ef4444; }
    h3 { color: #fff; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    p { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6; }
</style>